sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard<br/>(Module Federation)
    participant KServeCtrl as KServe Controller<br/>(llmisvc-controller)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>(LLM Runtime)
    participant EPP as llm-d EPP<br/>(Inference Scheduler)
    participant ODMC as odh-model-controller
    participant Envoy as Envoy Gateway
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy
    participant Authorino as Kuadrant/Authorino
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,Client: Workflow 1: LLM Model Deployment and Inference

    %% Authentication
    User->>Envoy: Access dashboard (HTTPS/443)
    Envoy->>AuthProxy: ext_authz delegation
    AuthProxy-->>Envoy: OIDC/OAuth token
    Envoy->>Dashboard: Forward with Bearer token

    %% Model deployment
    User->>Dashboard: Create LLMInferenceService via UI
    Dashboard->>KServeCtrl: Create LLMInferenceService CR

    KServeCtrl->>KServeCtrl: Reconcile: create Deployment/LeaderWorkerSet
    KServeCtrl->>vLLM: Create vLLM pods with model config
    KServeCtrl->>EPP: Create EPP Deployment (ext_proc)
    KServeCtrl->>KServeCtrl: Create InferencePool + HTTPRoute

    Note over vLLM: Download model from S3<br/>via storage-initializer<br/>(HTTPS/443, AWS IAM)

    vLLM->>vLLM: Load model weights, start serving

    ODMC->>ODMC: Watch InferenceService
    ODMC->>Envoy: Create HTTPRoute + Gateway EnvoyFilter
    ODMC->>Authorino: Create AuthPolicy for model endpoint
    ODMC->>ODMC: Create ServiceMonitor + KEDA ScaledObject

    %% Inference flow
    Client->>Envoy: POST /v1/completions (HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+)
    Envoy->>Authorino: Validate Bearer token / API key
    Authorino-->>Envoy: Auth OK
    Envoy->>EPP: ext_proc: select best endpoint
    EPP->>EPP: Score endpoints by queue depth,<br/>KV-cache utilization, latency prediction
    EPP-->>Envoy: Selected vLLM endpoint
    Envoy->>vLLM: Forward request to selected pod
    vLLM-->>Envoy: Streaming response (SSE)
    Envoy-->>Client: Streaming response (HTTPS)

    %% Monitoring
    Note over ODMC: ServiceMonitor scrapes<br/>vLLM metrics for Prometheus

