sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard
    participant NotebookCtrl as Kubeflow Notebook<br/>Controller
    participant ODHCtrl as ODH Notebook<br/>Controller
    participant Notebook as Notebook Pod<br/>(StatefulSet)
    participant Envoy as Envoy Gateway
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy
    participant DSPA as DSPA Instance
    participant Feast as Feature Store
    participant S3 as S3 Storage

    Note over User,S3: Workflow 2: Notebook Workbench Lifecycle

    %% Launch notebook
    User->>Envoy: Access dashboard (HTTPS/443)
    Envoy->>AuthProxy: ext_authz (OIDC/OAuth)
    AuthProxy-->>Envoy: Bearer token
    Envoy->>Dashboard: Forward authenticated request

    User->>Dashboard: Select workbench image,<br/>configure resources, launch
    Dashboard->>NotebookCtrl: Create Notebook CR in user namespace

    NotebookCtrl->>NotebookCtrl: Reconcile Notebook CR
    NotebookCtrl->>Notebook: Create StatefulSet + Service

    ODHCtrl->>ODHCtrl: Watch Notebook CR
    ODHCtrl->>Notebook: Inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar
    ODHCtrl->>Envoy: Create HTTPRoute for notebook access
    ODHCtrl->>ODHCtrl: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>(allow Gateway + monitoring ingress)

    %% Auto-inject connections
    ODHCtrl->>ODHCtrl: Detect DSPA in namespace
    ODHCtrl->>Notebook: Inject pipeline connection env vars
    ODHCtrl->>ODHCtrl: Detect Feast in namespace
    ODHCtrl->>Notebook: Inject feature_store.yaml ConfigMap

    %% User works
    User->>Envoy: Access notebook (HTTPS/443)
    Envoy->>AuthProxy: ext_authz
    AuthProxy-->>Envoy: Bearer token
    Envoy->>Notebook: Forward to notebook backend

    Notebook->>S3: Download training data (HTTPS/443, AWS IAM)
    Note over Notebook: Train model locally
    Notebook->>Feast: Query features (auto-injected connection)
    Notebook->>S3: Upload model artifacts

    %% Idle culling
    Note over ODHCtrl: Culling loop polls<br/>Jupyter kernel activity API
    ODHCtrl->>Notebook: No activity detected after timeout
    ODHCtrl->>NotebookCtrl: Scale StatefulSet replicas to 0

