sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard
    participant DSPAPI as DSP API Server
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>Controller
    participant Driver as DSP Driver
    participant Cache as Cache Server<br/>(Webhook)
    participant Launcher as DSP Launcher
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata
    participant PersAgent as Persistence Agent
    participant S3 as S3/Object Storage
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry
    participant KServe as KServe

    Note over User,KServe: Workflow 3: ML Pipeline Execution

    User->>Dashboard: Upload pipeline, configure run params
    Dashboard->>DSPAPI: Submit pipeline run

    DSPAPI->>DSPAPI: Store pipeline spec
    DSPAPI->>Argo: Create Argo Workflow CR

    Argo->>Argo: Orchestrate workflow steps

    loop Each Pipeline Step
        Argo->>Driver: Run Driver container
        Driver->>Cache: Check cache (webhook) -<br/>skip if cached result exists
        Driver->>MLMD: Create execution record (gRPC)
        Driver->>Driver: Resolve input artifacts

        Argo->>Launcher: Run Launcher container
        Launcher->>S3: Download input artifacts (HTTPS/443)
        Note over Launcher: Execute user container
        Launcher->>S3: Upload output artifacts (HTTPS/443)
        Launcher->>MLMD: Record output metadata (gRPC)
    end

    PersAgent->>Argo: Watch Workflow status (informers)
    PersAgent->>DSPAPI: Sync execution state

    %% Optional: register and deploy model
    Note over User: Pipeline outputs trained model
    User->>Dashboard: Register model from pipeline output
    Dashboard->>ModelReg: Create RegisteredModel +<br/>ModelVersion + ModelArtifact (REST/gRPC)
    ModelReg->>S3: Store artifact reference

    User->>Dashboard: Deploy model to serving
    Dashboard->>KServe: Create InferenceService CR
    KServe->>S3: Download model via storage-initializer

