sequenceDiagram
    participant User as ML Engineer
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard<br/>(eval-hub BFF)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub
    participant Kueue as Kueue
    participant EvalJob as Evaluation Job<br/>(lm-eval-harness)
    participant Sidecar as eval-runtime-sidecar
    participant vLLM as vLLM / KServe<br/>Model Endpoint
    participant S3 as S3 Storage
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking

    Note over User,MLflow: Workflow 4: Model Evaluation

    User->>Dashboard: Select model endpoint,<br/>choose benchmarks, submit eval
    Dashboard->>EvalHub: Create evaluation request

    EvalHub->>Kueue: Submit Workload for admission
    Kueue-->>EvalHub: Workload admitted
    EvalHub->>EvalJob: Create K8s Job<br/>(lm-evaluation-harness + sidecar)

    Sidecar->>S3: Download test datasets (HTTPS/443)
    Sidecar->>vLLM: Proxy inference requests<br/>with auth credentials

    loop Benchmark Execution
        EvalJob->>Sidecar: Send eval prompts
        Sidecar->>vLLM: Forward to model endpoint
        vLLM-->>Sidecar: Model responses
        Sidecar-->>EvalJob: Proxied responses
        EvalJob->>EvalHub: Report progress callback
    end

    EvalJob->>EvalHub: Final results
    EvalHub->>MLflow: Record metrics in experiment (REST)
    EvalHub->>EvalHub: Push artifacts to OCI registry
    EvalHub-->>Dashboard: Evaluation complete

    User->>Dashboard: View evaluation results
    Dashboard->>MLflow: Fetch experiment metrics
    Dashboard-->>User: Display benchmark scores,<br/>comparison charts

